display_name: Requisition transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_32 - Ariba Procurement - 2

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
WITH TMP_CEL_REQUISITION AS (
    SELECT 
        * ,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY "InitialUniqueName" 
            ORDER BY 
                CAST("VersionNumber" AS integer) DESC
        ) AS RN
    FROM "Requisition"
    WHERE 1=1
        AND "Requisition"."Active" = 'true'
        AND "Requisition"."StatusString" NOT IN ('Composing')
)
SELECT 
    'Requisition_' || "Requisition"."InitialUniqueName" as "ID",
    "Requisition"."ERPRequisitionID" as "ERPRequisitionID",
    "Requisition"."UniqueName" as "UniqueName",
    "Requisition"."IsForecast" as "IsForecast",
    "Requisition"."IsServiceRequisition" as "IsServiceRequisition",
    "Requisition"."StatusString" as "StatusString",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."TimeUpdated") as "TimeUpdated",
    "Requisition"."ApprovedState" as "ApprovedState",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."CreateDate") AS "CreateDate",
    "Requisition"."Name" as "Name",
    "Requisition"."Version" as "Version",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."ApprovedDate") AS "ApprovedDate",
    "Requisition"."PreviousApprovalRequestsVersion" as "PreviousApprovalRequestsVersion",
    cast("Requisition"."NumberBilled" as float) as "NumberBilled",
    cast("Requisition"."BudgetCheckStatus" as int) as "BudgetCheckStatus",
    "Requisition"."AreOrdersStuck" as "AreOrdersStuck",
    "Requisition"."PaymentTerms" as "PaymentTerms",
    cast("Requisition"."ApprovalRequestsVersion" as int) as "ApprovalRequestsVersion",
    "Requisition"."InitialUniqueName" as "InitialUniqueName",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."SubmitDate") AS "SubmitDate",
    "Requisition"."LastModified" as "LastModified",
    cast("Requisition"."NumberCleared" as float) as "NumberCleared",
    cast("Requisition"."VersionNumber" as int) as "VersionNumber",
    "Requisition"."Type" as "Type",
    "Requisition"."IsServiceOrder" as "IsServiceOrder",
    cast("Requisition"."SourcingStatus" as int) as "SourcingStatus",
    "Requisition"."ReceivedState" as "ReceivedState",
    "Requisition"."NumberReceivableOrders" as "NumberReceivableOrders",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("Requisition"."TimeCreated" as timestamp)) as "TimeCreated",
    --"Requisition"."Requester" as "Requester",                                              JSON FORMAT
    "Requisition"."OrderedState" as "OrderedState",
    "Requisition"."Active" as "Active",
    "Requisition"."PreviousVersion" as "PreviousVersion",
    "Requisition"."IsExternalReq" as "IsExternalReq",
    --"Requisition"."Preparer" as "Preparer",                                              JSON FORMAT
    cast("Requisition"."TotalCost_AmountInReportingCurrency" as float) as "TotalCostAmountInReportingCurrency",
    cast("Requisition"."TotalCost_ApproxAmountInBaseCurrency" as float) as "TotalCostApproxAmountInBaseCurrency",
    cast("Requisition"."TotalCost_Amount" as float) as "TotalCostAmount",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."TotalCost_ConversionDate") AS "TotalCostConversionDate",
    "Requisition"."TotalCost_Currency_UniqueName" as "TotalCostCurrencyUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."Requester_UniqueName" as "RequesterUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."ChangedBy_UniqueName" as "ChangedByUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."RealTimeBudgetResponse_UniqueName" as "RealTimeBudgetResponseUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."ProcurementUnit_UniqueName" as "ProcurementUnitUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."ReportingCurrency_UniqueName" as "ReportingCurrencyUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."CustomCatalogPurchaseOrg_UniqueName" as "CustomCatalogPurchaseOrgUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."PreviousVersion_UniqueName" as "PreviousVersionUniqueName",
    "Requisition"."Preparer_UniqueName" as "PreparerUniqueName",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."ResubmitDate") AS "ResubmitDate",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Requisition"."OrderedDate") AS "OrderedDate"
FROM TMP_CEL_REQUISITION AS "Requisition"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "Requisition"."RN" = 1
    --AND "Requisition"."Active" = 'true'
    --AND "InitialUniqueName" = 'PR8117'
